                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-43-off196 t17830723-43-cd197"></join> last, one watch, the inside and outside cases made of silver, value 2 l. one base metal chain, value 2 s. and one tortoise-shell snuff-box, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830723-43-victim505" type="victimName">
                     John 
