                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-43-defend503 t17830723-43-punish201"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. DEPUTY RECORDER.</p>
